## Limitations

The findings are based on available literature and may not encompass all perspectives on the ethical concerns of sharing health data online. Some articles may not be up-to-date, and the rapidly evolving nature of digital health technologies could introduce new ethical challenges not covered in the current literature. Additionally, the focus was primarily on English-language sources, which may limit the inclusion of global perspectives.